    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons who are paid or routinely employed to provide sexual services, or performances, as in the pornography industry, or as a prostitute. The term is often used to avoid or reduce negative connotations of such work, to indicate agency in the activity performed, or to evoke less charged service industries.</Note_Text>
